[b]Question :[/b] You'r server doesn't work on my computer...Why? [b]Answer :[/b] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,425280.msg3123255.html#msg3123255]Just Follow Instruction here, But this is only if you are using Windows 7 or Vista..[/url]

[b]Question :[/b] How can I change it so I can give people mod/admin/donator/owner? [b]Answer : [/b] Go to Client.java (In the source files) and search for Bashar, Replace my name with you'rs
[b]Question :[/b] What is the command to reset npc's? [b]Answer :[/b] The command is ::resetnpc
[b]Question :[/b] How to remove an item for donators only? [b]Answer :[/b] Get the items ID Example Santa hat is for donators, search in client.java for [code=java] if(wearID == 1050 && (donator != 1)) { // by Owner Bashar sM("You Need To Be A Donator To Wear This Item."); return false; } [/code] Just remove it
[b]Question :[/b] How can I change the client title and the ip? [b]Answer :[/b] To change the client title, search in GUI.java for [code=java]public static String frameTitlep[/code] After that you will see the clients title "PkPlanet Client" change that to you'r servers name To change the ip, Search in GUI.java for "Serverip = "127.0.0.1";" Replace 127.0.0.1 with you'r server ip
[b]Question :[/b] How can I make myself mod/admin/owner/hidden owner? [b]Answer :[/b] Go to Players>Chracters>YOU'RACCOUNT.txt Then look for "character-rights = 3" 0 = Normal Player, 1 = Modeterator, 2 = Adminstrator, 3 = Owner, 4 = Hidden Owner
[b]Question :[/b] In the Donator shop the items are 0 how can I change that? [b]Answer :[/b] Go to Source>Config>Shops.cfg Search for "shop = 54 @gre@Donators Items!" It should appear like this [code=java]shop = 54 @gre@Donators Items! 2 2 1050 0 1053 0 1055 0 1057 0 1038 0 1040 0 1042 0 1044 0 1046 0 1048 0 8102 0 6891 0 6893 0 6898 0 6895 0 6894 0 6891 0 6897 0 16005 0 16004 0 16003 0 1295 0 8100 0 13665 0 8002 0 [/code] Change all the 0 to the amount you want the shop to sell!
[b]Question :[/b] How can I change the starter arena? [b]Answer :[/b] Go to Player.java and search for [code=java]toX = 3087; toY = 3492;[/code]
Change them to the place you want the starter to start...
Thanks for looking at my server! :):):):):):)
- Bashar
